---
import type { Lang } from '../lib/locales';
import SocialLinks from './SocialLinks.astro';

interface Props {
  lang?: Lang;
}

const { lang = 'en' } = Astro.props;
const portraitUrl = 'https://github.com/anneincontext.png?size=360';
---

{lang === 'zh' ? (
  <>
    <section class="page-heading about-hero">
      <div class="about-media">
        <figure class="about-portrait" aria-label="Anne Li">
          <img
            src={portraitUrl}
            alt=""
            width="220"
            height="220"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </figure>
        <SocialLinks lang="zh" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-copy">
        <p>
          我是 安妮。过去十年里，我做过前端工程师，也经历过创业公司、小团队、大型科技公司、自由职业，以及数字游民不同的工作方式。
        </p>
        <p>
          除了写代码之外，我也长期参与开发者社区，组织活动、分享经验、认识来自不同背景的人。
        </p>
        <p>
          我一直觉得，能够帮助别人是一件很有成就感的事情，而人与人的连接，往往比技术本身更吸引我。
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-profile">
      <div class="about-lede">
        <h3>我在做什么</h3>
        <p>
          我喜欢做不同世界之间的连接者（Connector）。
        </p>
        <p>
          无论是中文与英文、开发者与产品团队、程序员与非程序员，还是线上与线下社区，我都乐于帮助不同背景的人建立共同的理解。
        </p>
        <p>
          Developer Experience、技术内容、开发者活动、社区运营、产品反馈循环……这些在我看来，本质上都是连接的不同形式。它们让复杂的技术更容易被理解，让好的产品更容易被发现，也让开发者的声音能够回到产品团队。
        </p>
      </div>
      <ul class="about-facts" aria-label="经历亮点">
        <li><span>10+ 年</span> 创业公司 × 小公司  × 大厂 × 自由职业 × 数字游民</li>
        <li>
          <span>20+ 国家</span>
          <span class="country-flags" aria-label="走访国家与地区">🇨🇳🇸🇬🇹🇭🇮🇩🇲🇾🇻🇳🇯🇵🇳🇵🇬🇧🇪🇸🇵🇹🇫🇷🇳🇱🇩🇪🇨🇿🇦🇹🇭🇺🇮🇹🇻🇦🇬🇷🇹🇷🇦🇪</span>
          我去过 20 多个国家，还有很多地方等待解锁～
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

  </>
) : (
  <>
    <section class="page-heading about-hero">
      <div class="about-media">
        <figure class="about-portrait" aria-label="Anne Li">
          <img
            src={portraitUrl}
            alt=""
            width="220"
            height="220"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </figure>
        <SocialLinks lang="en" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-copy">
        <p>
          I am Anne Li. Over the past decade, I have worked as a frontend engineer
          across startups, smaller teams, and large technology companies, while also spending time as a freelancer and digital nomad.
        </p>
        <p>
          Beyond engineering, I've always been active in developer communities. I enjoy bringing people together, sharing what I've learned, and making complex ideas easier to understand.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-profile">
      <div class="about-lede">
        <h3>What I Do</h3>
        <p>I like being a connector.</p>

        <p>Between Chinese and English. Between developers and product teams. Between programmers and non-programmers. Between communities, ideas, and the people who can benefit from them.</p>

        <p>Developer Experience, technical writing, community events, product feedback, and developer education are simply different ways of building those connections.</p>

      </div>
      <ul class="about-facts" aria-label="Highlights">
        <li><span>10+ years</span> engineering and developer ecosystem experience since 2016</li>
        <li>
          <span>20+ countries</span>
          <span class="country-flags" aria-label="Countries and regions visited">🇨🇳🇸🇬🇹🇭🇮🇩🇲🇾🇻🇳🇯🇵🇳🇵🇬🇧🇪🇸🇵🇹🇫🇷🇳🇱🇩🇪🇨🇿🇦🇹🇭🇺🇮🇹🇻🇦🇬🇷🇹🇷🇦🇪</span>
          I have visited 20+ countries, with more to come
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

  </>
)}
